      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i get that they're considered flawed now, but for the debate i really need to nail the \"logic\" they used so i can argue it effectively. can you expand on the \"property value\" argument? like, how did they specifically link racial demographics to the idea of economic stability or \"neighborhood character\"? i want to understand the actual mechanics of their reasoning so i can present a more convincing case for the assignment.",
